text: Mouni Roy (born 28 September 1985) is an Indian actress, singer, Kathak dancer and former model. She is mainly known for her work in Indian television and Hindi-language movies. Her popular works are Mahadev, Naagin and Gold. == References == == Other websites == * * * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Indian television actors Category:Indian movie actors
